Module com.example.organizer
Package com.bookclub.mao

Class ReviewMAO

java.lang.Object
com.bookclub.mao.ReviewMAO
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.bookclub.iao.IReviewAO
public class ReviewMAO extends Object implements com.bookclub.iao.IReviewAO
Mock Access Object (MAO) for handling in-memory Review operations. Implements the IReviewAO interface to provide methods for managing reviews, including adding, updating, deleting, and retrieving reviews.
